---
title: Seared Steak Strips with Noodles, Charred Sweetcorn and Veggies
description: Quick, delicious and easy to prep, this sizzling one-pan steak stir-fry will be on the table in 30 minutes flat. Charring the sweetcorn adds a lovely texture to the dish which works brilliantly with juicy seared steak, crunchy peanuts, and velvety noodles. Bursting with fresh zingy flavours and packed with fresh good-for you ingredients, this easy recipe will take your stir-fry game to the next level.
